\ Test geth and seth
[ 10 20 30 ] |myVector|

\ Test geth
$myVector 0 geth print  \ Should print 10
$myVector 1 geth print  \ Should print 20
$myVector 2 geth print  \ Should print 30

\ Test seth
$myVector 1 99 seth |myVector|
$myVector 1 geth print  \ Should print 99

\ Verify full vector
$myVector print
